      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition, presenting as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish and absolutely no scratches, chips, or dings. Inside, the cabin is pristine; the upholstery shows no signs of wear, the controls are crisp, and it still retains that new-car scent. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been garage-kept and maintained with an open checkbook. For a buyer seeking the absolute best example of this model without any compromises, this is the one.",
