      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine and a factory Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission. This enthusiast-owned example has been optimized for longevity with completed rod bearing services and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul. The chassis integrity is secured via a reinforced rear subframe, addressing the model's primary structural weak point. Performance is sharpened by a limited-slip differential and a refreshed suspension featuring Bilstein B6 dampers and polyurethane bushings for precise turn-in. While the exterior shows minor road patina, the drivetrain remains in peak operational form, delivering a linear power band up to the 8,000 RPM redline. All service records are available to verify the mechanical pedigree.",
